---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Tid till FIRE"
  description="Se hur en extra kostnad eller ett extra sparande påverkar hur många år du jobbar innan FIRE."
>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-6 space-y-4">
    <header class="space-y-2">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Tid till FIRE</h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] max-w-3xl">
        Avkastning är <span class="text-[var(--text)] font-medium">real</span> (efter inflation).
        Vi antar sparande <span class="text-[var(--text)] font-medium">i början av varje år</span>.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-4 space-y-3">
      <div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
        <label class="text-sm">Din ålder
          <input id="startAge" type="number" value="30"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 outline-none focus:border-[var(--gold)]" />
        </label>

        <label class="text-sm">Månadskostnad (kr/mån)
          <input id="monthlySpend" type="number" value="30000"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 outline-none focus:border-[var(--gold)]" />
        </label>

        <label class="text-sm">Sparkvot (% av netto)
          <input id="saveRate" type="number" value="35" step="0.1"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 outline-none focus:border-[var(--gold)]" />
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
        <label class="text-sm">Avkastning (realt, %/år)
          <input id="returnPct" type="number" value="5" step="0.1"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 outline-none focus:border-[var(--gold)]" />
        </label>

        <label class="text-sm">Säker uttagsnivå (%/år)
          <input id="swPct" type="number" value="4" step="0.1"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 outline-none focus:border-[var(--gold)]" />
        </label>

        <label class="text-sm">Maxålder i simulering
          <input id="maxAge" type="number" value="80"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 outline-none focus:border-[var(--gold)]" />
        </label>

        <label class="text-sm">Startkapital (kr)
         <input id="startCapital" type="number" value="0"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 outline-none focus:border-[var(--gold)]" />
        </label>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">
        FIRE-mål beräknas som <code class="text-[var(--text)]">årlig utgift / uttagsnivå</code>. (Ex: 4% → 25× årsutgift)
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-4 space-y-4">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Beslutet du testar</h2>
        <button id="loadExamples"
          class="rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-soft)] border border-[var(--border)] px-3 py-2 hover:border-[var(--gold)] text-sm">
          Ladda exempel
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
        <label class="text-sm">Typ
          <select id="deltaType"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 outline-none focus:border-[var(--gold)]">
            <option value="spend">Extra kostnad</option>
            <option value="save">Extra sparande</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <label class="text-sm">Belopp (kr/mån)
          <input id="deltaAmount" type="number" value="1000"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 outline-none focus:border-[var(--gold)]" />
        </label>

        <label class="text-sm">Namn (valfritt)
          <input id="deltaLabel" type="text" value="Bil"
            class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/20 px-3 py-2 outline-none focus:border-[var(--gold)]" />
        </label>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">
        Extra kostnad påverkar både din årsutgift (FIRE-mål) och din sparförmåga. Extra sparande påverkar bara sparandet.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-4 space-y-2">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Resultat</h2>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface-soft)]/50 p-4 text-sm space-y-2">
        <p class="text-[var(--text)]">
          <span class="text-[var(--text-muted)]">Baseline:</span>
          FIRE vid <span id="baseFireAge" class="font-semibold">–</span>
          (<span id="baseYearsLeft" class="font-semibold">–</span> år kvar).
        </p>

        <p class="text-[var(--text)]">
          <span class="text-[var(--text-muted)]">Med beslutet:</span>
          FIRE vid <span id="newFireAge" class="font-semibold">–</span>
          (<span id="newYearsLeft" class="font-semibold">–</span> år kvar).
        </p>

        <div class="border-t border-[var(--border)] pt-2">
          <p class="text-[var(--text)]">
            Effekten blir: <span id="deltaYears" class="font-semibold">–</span>
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]" id="deltaExplain"></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-4 space-y-2">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Kapital över tid</h2>

      <div class="h-[520px] flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-black/15 p-3">
        <div class="flex-1 min-h-0 relative">
          <canvas id="chart"></canvas>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-muted)]">
          Linjer: kapital och FIRE-mål. När kapitalet korsar målet är du “FIRE” enligt antagandena.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] bg-[var(--surface)] p-4 space-y-2">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Detaljer</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="min-w-full text-sm">
          <thead class="text-left text-[var(--text-muted)]">
            <tr class="border-b border-[var(--border)]">
              <th class="py-2 pr-4">Scenario</th>
              <th class="py-2 pr-4">Årsutgift</th>
              <th class="py-2 pr-4">Årssparande</th>
              <th class="py-2 pr-4">FIRE-mål</th>
              <th class="py-2 pr-4">FIRE-ålder</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="detailsRows"></tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)] pt-2">
        Förenklad modell. Syftet är insikt, inte prognos.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script type="module" src="/js/tidTillFire.client.js"></script>
</BaseLayout>
